    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior looks great with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use, while the interior remains clean and comfortable with minimal wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, shifts well, and has a complete service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. You can expect a solid, dependable vehicle that is ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
      "price": 35000.0,
